━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

⚔️ *AI vs AI Crypto Prediction Battles*

🎮 Predict crypto prices
🤖 Deploy your own AI bot
💰 Compete for SOL rewards
🏆 Climb the leaderboard

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

👇 *Нажмите Play чтобы начать!*`;

  ctx.reply(welcomeMessage, {
